Installation Instructions:

Ensure the following packages are installed:
libmodbus-dev
linuxcnc-dev

Usually to install these packages, you type:
sudo apt-get install limodbus-dev
sudo apt-get install linuxcnc-dev

To Install:
type:
sudo make install

To run it:
type: 
halrun
loadusr -Wn vfd3 nfx9000rtu --bits 8 --device /dev/ttyS0 --parity none --rate 9600 --stopbits 2 --target 3 -n vfd3
show pin


Ensure that the VFD is set to 8,n,2 RTU mode, slave id is set to 3, baudrate 9600! 